  "description": "<p><strong>#able work on weekends and public holiday</strong></p><p>Ensure accurate and timely delivery and collection of goods to established schedules and delivery routes.</p><p>Loading and unloading of goods.</p><p>Review orders before and after delivery to ensure that delivery is correct and complete, and charges are correct (COD).</p><p>Provide good customer service when fulfilling deliveries.</p><p>Upkeep cleanliness and maintenance of the company vehicle.</p><p>Perform proper stock keeping and handling.</p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><p>At least a GCE \"N\" Levels or its equivalent</p><p>At least 3 years of driving experience</p><p>Holds a Class 3 or Class 4 license with good driving records</p>",
